WEBVTT

00:00.445 --> 00:04.545
Add an "ly" to some adjectives to form an adverb.

00:14.138 --> 00:16.317
He is a bad man.

00:17.661 --> 00:20.274
Also, he drives badly.

00:24.371 --> 00:27.789
This turtle is slow.

00:29.046 --> 00:32.835
This turtle walks slowly.

00:36.737 --> 00:38.235
The cheetah is quick.

00:39.375 --> 00:41.183
The cheetah runs quickly.

00:45.085 --> 00:47.079
This is easy!

00:48.149 --> 00:50.699
The dog can do this easily.

